</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>警方最新智能搜救「3R」裝備    R-Map + R-Watch + R-Cam</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/17/3r/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=3r</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jun 2022 04:58:14 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1105204</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>疫情下有不少市民都喜愛到郊外登山遠足，但發生的登山意外事故亦相應增加。為提高搜救效率，研發高科技「3R」裝備， [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>疫情下有不少市民都喜愛到郊外登山遠足，但發生的登山意外事故亦相應增加。為提高搜救效率，研發高科技「3R」裝備，協助攀山搜救。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1105320 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-10.56.10-1-694x460.png" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-10.56.10-1-694x460.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-10.56.10-1-768x509.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-10.56.10-1.png 902w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287220620_704334877316712_1196768385619944779_n.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1105358" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287220620_704334877316712_1196768385619944779_n.png" alt="" width="662" height="368" /></a></p><p>日前，警方聯同民安隊和飛行服務隊，到西貢北潭湧進行實地救援演練，期間向傳媒展示當局成功研發的「3R」裝備，救援人員戴上自行研發的電子搜救地圖 R-Map、與科企共同研發，可記錄心跳和身處位置的 R-Watch，並可直播 4K 超高清影像的攝錄鏡頭 R-Cam。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1105318 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.17-694x435.png" alt="" width="694" height="435" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.17-694x435.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.17-1280x802.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.17-768x481.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.17-1536x962.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.17-2048x1282.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1105319 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.38-694x478.png" alt="" width="694" height="478" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.38-694x478.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.38-1280x882.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.38-768x529.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.38-1536x1059.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-11.32.38.png 1996w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<span class="s2"><a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1653305-20220616.htm?spTabChangeable=0">RTHK</a></span> 截圖）</p><p>由警務處資訊系統部自行研發的 R-Map 會收集裝備所有資料，R-Cam 現場直播 4K 超高清影像，並透過 5G 網絡實時加密傳送至指揮中心，能同時讓拯救人員掌握同袍方位、身體情況和周遭環境等，有助協調人手資源，以更快速度救援傷者。</p><p>警務處資訊系統部高級督察黃迪奇表示，智能手錶 R-Watch 是警方和一間科技公司合作研發，充電後可使用六至八小時。他又指，本港警方是全球首支將智能手錶用於搜救的執法部隊。</p><p>警方去年共錄得 951 宗攀山拯救行動，較 2019 年大升約 3.4 倍。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1653305-20220616.htm?spTabChangeable=0">RTHK</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
